Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紫阳花玉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.33,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私はもうあの頃の私じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是那时的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.57,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,とどめよ　こいつを一人で退治して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止它 凭己之力消灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.15,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,それを証明する
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,来证明我的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.96,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,上等じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
