Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,还轮不到你来说我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.73,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しょうがないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
