Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.46,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなやつさっさと退治する
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快把这家伙收拾了
