Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,火钵小姐 水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.22,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと温い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不够热
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.19,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是
