Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.69,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰にも言わない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会告诉别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.11,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.22,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ教えてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就告诉你吧
