Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:13.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个 死色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.56,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっとは仲良くなったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,关系变好些了吧
